{"title":"Sour Bicycles Space Cake All Road","link":"https://theradavist.com/sour-bicycles-space-cake-all-road/","date":1731336550000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Space_Cake_All-Road.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Space_Cake_All-Road.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Space_Cake_All-Road.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Space_Cake_All-Road.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>As previewed in our <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2024-bespoked-uk-handmade-bicycle-show-part-01/\" target=\"_blank\">Bespoked 2024 coverage</a>, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/sour-bicycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Sour Bicycles</a> has just announced the <a href=\"https://sour.bike/bikes/road/space-cake/\" target=\"_blank\">Space Cake All-Road</a> model. Let’s check it out…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-11.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-11.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-8.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-8.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Space Cake Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Sizes Small through X-Large</li>\n<li>Frameset 1.299,00 €</li>\n<li>Complete Ultegra Di2 2x 5.999,00 €</li>\n<li>Fender and rack mounts</li>\n<li>Recommended tire size 28mm – 38mm</li>\n<li>Two water bottle mounts inside frame, a third bottle mount under the downtube</li>\n<li>AXS/Di2 ready cable routing</li>\n<li>Internal brake hose routing</li>\n<li>External mechanical cable routing</li>\n<li>27,2mm seatpost diameter for maximum comfort</li>\n<li>SRAM Transmission compatible dropouts (“UDH”)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/SourSpaceCakeGeo.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/SourSpaceCakeGeo.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/SourSpaceCakeGeo.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/SourSpaceCakeGeo.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Geometry</h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-2.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-13.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-13.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-13.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-13.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/2024-Bespoked-Sour-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><span>﻿</span><span><span></span></span><span></span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Designed with endurance in mind, the Space Cake is all about going longer. With a road-focused frame built to handle big miles, it’s comfortable, light, and efficient. With fenders, dynamo routing, and clearance for big tires that will make the ride more plush but not so big that they bog you down, the Space Cake is a ally for winter training or even rides like Paris-Brest-Paris.</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://sour.bike/bikes/road/space-cake/\" target=\"_blank\">Sour Bicycles</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/sour-bicycles-space-cake-all-road/\">Sour Bicycles Space Cake All Road</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"217e4a99c5c19e439c937c8b034292ecb18f6c0ee6af36c09a6cc6996368e42c","category":"Cycling"}